<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New User Registration - Flying Duchess Pet-Sitting</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Flying Duchess Pet-Sitting System</h1>
            <h2>New User Registration</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello Admin,</p>
            <p>A new user has registered and is pending approval:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{firstName}} {{lastName}}</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
                <li><strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</li>
                <li><strong>Registration Date:</strong> {{registrationDate}}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please review and approve or reject this user in the admin panel.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>Flying Duchess Pet-Sitting System</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Flying Duchess Pet-Sitting. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
